The capital city is Opuwo. The name comes from the Kunene River. It forms the northern border with Angola. Kunene's western edge is the Atlantic Ocean. The region has seven constituencies: * Epupa * Kamanjab * Khorixas * Opuwo Rural * Opuwo Urban * Outjo * Sesfontein ==References== Category:Regions of Namibia
